  "prompt": "Which are top classified websites in Saudi Arabia?",
  "response": "As of my last update in October 2023, there are several popular classified websites in Saudi Arabia that cater to a wide range of needs, from buying and selling goods to job postings and real estate listings. Here are some of the top classified websites in Saudi Arabia:\n\n1. **Haraj.com.sa**  \n   - One of the most popular classified websites in Saudi Arabia. It offers a wide range of categories, including cars, real estate, electronics, and services.\n\n2. **OpenSooq.com**  \n   - A widely used platform across the Middle East, including Saudi Arabia. It offers listings for cars, real estate, jobs, and more.\n\n3. **Expatriates.com**  \n   - Primarily focused on the expatriate community in Saudi Arabia, this site offers classifieds for jobs, housing, and services.\n\n4. **Souq.com** (now part of Amazon.sa)  \n   - While primarily an e-commerce platform, it also has sections for classified listings.\n\n5. **OLX Saudi Arabia**  \n   - A global classifieds platform with a strong presence in Saudi Arabia. It offers listings for cars, real estate, jobs, and household items.\n\n6. **SaudiSale.com**  \n   - Focused on selling cars, but also includes sections for other classified listings like real estate and electronics.\n\n7. **Mubawab.sa**  \n   - Specializes in real estate listings, including properties for sale and rent.\n\n8. **AqarMap.com**  \n   - Another popular real estate platform in Saudi Arabia, offering detailed property listings.\n\n9. **SaudiList.com**  \n   - A classifieds platform that offers a variety of categories, including cars, jobs, and real estate.\n\n10. **Al Tawteen**  \n    - A job portal that also has sections for classified listings, particularly focused on employment opportunities.\n\nPlease note that the popularity and functionality of these websites can change over time, so it's a good idea to check them directly for the most current information and features.",
  "temperature": 1.0,
